Learn Finnish While You Sleep: Orders and instructions in Finnish
Osaatko käskeä suomeksi? Can you give orders / instructions in Finnish? like a native Finnish speaker even like learning Finnish while you sleep 
in this section you can learn the imperative when talking to one person - both positive forms (e.g. "Talk!") and negative forms (e.g. "Don't talk!")
